OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FThames Water boss says     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbills need to rise by 40%  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of Thames Water has told the  
OL,6, BBC customer bills need to rise by 40% 
OL,7, by 2030 to pay for improvements.       
OL,9,F"That is the price customers have to   
OL,10,Fpay for the investment in our          
OL,11,Finfrastructure that's needed," he said.
OL,13,FThe firm is in a race to find extra    
OL,14,Fcash after its investors said they     
OL,15,Fwould not give the struggling water    
OL,16,Fgiant more money unless bills rise.    
OL,18,FThe regulator, whose approval is needed
OL,19,Ffor any price rises, has so far pushed 
OL,20,Fback on substantial bill increases.    
